title: UK billionaire on board missing Titanic submersible, family confirms
description: UK billionaire Hamish Harding is one of five people on board a missing tourist submersible used to take people to see the wreck of the Titanic.

title: What we know about the passengers on board missing Titanic submersible
description: A UK billionaire, French submersible pilot and the CEO of a company that provides crewed submersibles are believed to be three of the people on board a missing vessel.

title: Commercial submarine goes missing near Titanic wreck
description: A commercial submarine has gone missing near the site of wreck of the Titanic, Sky News understands.

title: Nearly 170 dead as northern India swelters in heatwave
description: A heatwave in India has left 166 people dead in just a few days, according to state officials.

title: China's President Xi meets US secretary of state in bid to ease tensions
description: China's President Xi Jinping has met US secretary of state Antony Blinken in Beijing - as the world's two biggest economies look to cool rising tensions.

title: Jailed Putin critic faces 30 more years in prison on new 'extremism' charges as new trial begins
description: Alexei Navalny - the jailed critic of Vladimir Putin - has appeared in court in Russia on new "extremism" charges that could extend his prison term by decades.

title: Three dead and 29 injured in Israeli West Bank raid
description: Three Palestinians have died and 29 others have been injured during a raid by Israeli troops in the occupied West Bank.
